# Gradewise AI — Cursor Project Rules

> **Canonical rule files** live in `.agent/rules/` and `.claude/rules/` (mirrored). Read the specialized file for your task — this file is the quick index.

## Rule Map

| File | When to read |
|------|--------------|
| **`standards_rules.md`** | **Policies 1–5: deps · structure · naming · DRY · security/infra/testing** |
| `project_rules.md` | Repo layout, Docker, CI, commands, routes, env |
| `domain_rules.md` | RBAC, assessments, multilingual, XAI, business logic |
| `backend_rules.md` | `grade-wise-ai-backend-fastify/**/*.ts` |
| `frontend_rules.md` | `grade-wise-ai-frontend-next/**` |
| `ui.md` | Pure Tailwind v4 tokens, theme, a11y, `lib/ui.js` catalog |
| `workflow_rules.md` | Before commit — build/lint/test gates |
| `antigravity_rules.md` | Antigravity SDK agents only (not app code) |

Also see **`MIGRATION.md`** for modernization changelog.

Paths: `.agent/rules/` · `.claude/rules/` · root `ANTIGRAVITY_RULES.md`

---

## Repository

| App | Path | Stack |
|-----|------|-------|
| Backend | `grade-wise-ai-backend-fastify/` | Fastify 5 · TS 6 · Drizzle · PostgreSQL · Redis · BullMQ · AI SDK 6 · Vitest |
| Frontend | `grade-wise-ai-frontend-next/` | Next.js 16 · React 19 · Tailwind 4 · Zustand · TanStack Query · Playwright |
| Infra | `docker-compose.yml` | PostgreSQL 17 (pgvector) · Redis 8 · MinIO · api · worker · web · Node 24 |

**Deprecated:** `grade-wise-ai-backend-v2/` (Express) — do not use.

---

## Commands

```bash
# Infrastructure
docker compose up -d postgres redis minio

# Frontend (port 3000)
cd grade-wise-ai-frontend-next && npm run dev

# Backend API (port 5005)
cd grade-wise-ai-backend-fastify && npm run dev

# Backend worker (when USE_ASYNC_JOBS=true)
cd grade-wise-ai-backend-fastify && npm run dev:worker
```

| Check | Command | Directory |
|-------|---------|-----------|
| FE build | `npm run build` | `grade-wise-ai-frontend-next/` |
| FE lint | `npm run lint` | `grade-wise-ai-frontend-next/` |
| FE E2E | `npm run test:e2e` | `grade-wise-ai-frontend-next/` |
| BE typecheck | `npm run typecheck` | `grade-wise-ai-backend-fastify/` |
| BE build | `npm run build` | `grade-wise-ai-backend-fastify/` |
| BE tests | `npm test` | `grade-wise-ai-backend-fastify/` |

Copy `.env.example` → `.env` (backend) and `.env.local` (frontend) before first run.

---

## Non-Negotiables (see `standards_rules.md`)

1. **Policy 1 — Dependencies:** Latest stable; verify build/lint/test/typecheck.
2. **Policy 2 — Structure:** Backend `modules/<domain>/` · Frontend `features/<domain>/` · `schemas/` (not `scheema/`).
3. **Policy 3 — Naming:** camelCase · PascalCase components · kebab-case folders.
4. **Policy 4 — DRY:** Extract on 2nd use; reuse shared modules in standards.
5. **Policy 5 — Security:** httpOnly cookie auth · Google idToken verify · no JWT in localStorage · CI/tests.

